<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Strava Coach - AI Training Analysis</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 32px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .features {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 32px 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .features h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            color: #666;
        }
        .features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .features li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-strava {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fc4c02;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-strava:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(252, 76, 2, 0.3);
        }
        .settings {
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .settings-note {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .config-values {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: monospace;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ðŸš´ Strava Coach</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">AI-Powered Training Analysis</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h3>What this app does:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Connects to your Strava account</li>
                <li>Analyzes your cycling activities</li>
                <li>Calculates power zones & training stress</li>
                <li>Tracks heart rate zones & drift</li>
                <li>Generates weekly training summaries</li>
                <li>Formats data for AI coaching analysis</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/auth/strava" class="btn-strava">
            Connect with Strava
        </a>
        
        <div class="settings">
            <p class="settings-note">Default Training Settings:</p>
            <div class="config-values">
                FTP: 250W | HR Max: 180bpm (customizable after login)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>